                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Swift Point"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/bf8e655a65a1e61d133e9c59f9aef5b5_2980262734863829452.png",
                "id": "talent46293",
                "key": "Frosty Interjection ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Frosty Interjection "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. Attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Onslaught Stance</span> to this character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Onslaught Stance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters affected by <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bond of Life</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/25e4bcd70e5c79ed88012c83939e6a12_6507341974873059211.png",
                "id": "talent47773",
                "key": "Thorny Onslaught ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Thorny Onslaught "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After this character uses a Skill:</span> Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bond of Life</span> to the opponent's active character with <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> equal to (this Skill's finalized DMG total -2). (Max 5 stacks)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Bond of Life</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is healed:</span> This effect will be consumed once for every <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> it has to negate 1 HP of healing received. (Cannot negate revivals, increases in Max HP, and healing caused by redistribution of HP)<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack, no stack limit).</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/1ab78a4e226b75e7739eee3d3b8ea8aa_1682791556042189046.png",
                "id": "talent3636",
                "key": "Blood-Bonded Shadow ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Blood-Bonded Shadow "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_833794437622777729.png",
                "id": "talent3239",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong><br>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6666533510120436285.png",
